        "startTime": 16026,
        "endTime": 20199,
        "slowStartTime": 24189,
        "slowEndTime": 30523
    },
    {
        "text": "Three, every character should want something, even if it is only a glass of water.",
        "startTime": 22138,
        "endTime": 27491,
        "slowStartTime": 33357,
        "slowEndTime": 41462
    },
    {
        "text": "Four, every sentence must do one of two things,...",
        "startTime": 29410,
        "endTime": 32748,
        "slowStartTime": 44265,
        "slowEndTime": 49347
