        "endTime": 49713,
        "slowStartTime": 71901,
        "slowEndTime": 74794
    },
    {
        "text": "...in order that the reader may see what they are made of.",
        "startTime": 49903,
        "endTime": 53027,
        "slowStartTime": 75005,
        "slowEndTime": 79766
    },
    {
        "text": "Seven, write to please just one person.",
        "startTime": 54961,
        "endTime": 57726,
        "slowStartTime": 82592,
        "slowEndTime": 86814
    },
    {
        "text": "If you open a window and make love to the world, so to speak,...",
